headline: United States Orthodontics Market Research, Treatment Trends & Forecast Report 2025-2033
summary: The United States Orthodontics Market, valued at USD 2.04 billion in 2024, is projected to surge to USD 5.02 billion by 2033, driven by a CAGR of 10.5%. This growth is fuelled by increasing awareness of dental aesthetics, advancements in clear aligners, and a rising demand for early orthodontic treatments among children and adolescents.
